**6. Insertion Sort**
```java
public static void sort(IntTracker[] arr) {
    for (int i = 1; i < arr.length; i++) {
        IntTracker key = arr[i];
        int j = i - 1;
        while (j >= 0 && arr[j].getValue() > key.getValue()) {
            arr[j + 1] = arr[j];
            j--;
        }
        arr[j + 1] = key;
    }
}
