**21. Reconstruct Itinerary**
```java
public static String[] reconstructItinerary(String[][] tickets) {
    Map<String, String> map = new HashMap<>();
    Set<String> arrivals = new HashSet<>();
    for (String[] t : tickets) { map.put(t[0], t[1]); arrivals.add(t[1]); }
    String city = map.keySet().stream().filter(k -> !arrivals.contains(k)).findFirst().get();
    List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
    while (city != null) { result.add(city); city = map.get(city); }
    return result.toArray(new String[0]);
}
```

